lippy` reports that `clippy` is no longer available via `crates.io`.\r\n\r\nSorry if this is the wrong repo to report MSI installer issues; with 190 repos in the group, it can be hard to find the right one.", "closed_by": null, "reactions": {"url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/101993/reactions", "total_count": 0, "+1": 0, "-1": 0, "laugh": 0, "hooray": 0, "confused": 0, "heart": 0, "rocket": 0, "eyes": 0}, "timeline_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rust-lang/rust/issues/101993/timeline", "performed_via_github_app": null, "state_reason": null}